column2: It was filial tenderness that gave the name.
column3: It was filial tenderness that gave the name.

column2: I make but a poor figure at composition, my head is much too fickle, my thoughts are running after birds' eggs, play and trifles till I get vexed with myself.

column2: It almost seems a mistake, but it was not.
